onboardingBanner.title: Welcome to the Vodafone Business Managed IoT Connectivity Platform,
onboardingBannerDescription1: Whether you’re expanding your existing IoT estate or starting your IoT journey, we make it simple to deploy and manage IoT connectivity. We have recently upgraded the user experience, allowing you to configure and perform day-to-day operations faster. You can easily manage your SIMs and generate various reports to support your daily activities.
onboardingBannerDescription2: Our platform evolves as your business needs grow and we are constantly developing the platform to release new features. Customer feedback is very important to us, and we would be grateful if you could share your experience through the feedback surveys.
onboardingBanner.description1: Welcome to the Vodafone Business Managed IoT Connectivity Platform.
onboardingBanner.description2: We have made some changes to improve your experience, which will allow you to have better visibility of your IoT SIMs and have faster access to streamline your operations.
onboardingBanner.description3: You will be using a BETA version of our platform, and we plan to improve and deploy new features in the near future. We would appreciate if you could share your experience by completing our feedback surveys, and please let us know if you have any issues.
onboardingBanner.description4: To discover what you can do watch our introduction video, take the tour, or visit the help section for further support.
welcomeTour.title: IoT Connectivity
welcomeTour.textDescriptions.step0: The Dashboard allows you to get a quick view of information. Each widget allows you to dive deeper into the information if you want to see more.
welcomeTour.textDescriptions.oldStep0: The Dashboard allows you to get a quick view of information. Each widget allows you to dive deeper into the information if you want to see more. These widgets cover Total SIMs, Top service profiles, Saved searches and Operations.
welcomeTour.textDescriptions.stepService: Some Widgets may have multiple views of data (depending on your organisation's settings). The last view used on these widgets will be retained for the next time you load the Dashboard.
welcomeTour.textDescriptions.step1: The menus on the left and top of the screen allow you to access the main functions of the Vodafone Business Managed IoT Connectivity Platform and also access helpful information such as Help and Support, Notifications and also your User Preferences.
welcomeTour.textDescriptions.step2: The SIM List is where you can see all of your SIMs. If you have been brought to the SIM list from another area (such as a dashboard widget) then the list will be pre-filtered. If you come to the SIM List from the left-menu, then it will simply show all of you SIMs.
welcomeTour.textDescriptions.step3: Please click on the highlighted 'Filters' button to proceed.
welcomeTour.textDescriptions.step4: You can use the Filters to refine the contents of the SIM list. Using the 'Manage Filters' button you can add and remove a wide range of Filters to help you get your SIM list refined just the way you want it.
welcomeTour.textDescriptions.step5: Any of the columns in the SIM List can be rearranged into any order you like by dragging and dropping them. You can also sort any columns you like. Finally, if you'd like to see even more columns of data you can add them via the 'Customise Table' button.
welcomeTour.textDescriptions.step6: Using the New Action button you can find a range of actions you can perform on a SIM. Sometimes an option will be unavailable, this is because the Vodafone Business Managed IoT Connectivity Platform is smart enough to only allow actions that can be performed against the SIM you are looking at. The information icon next to the Action will tell you the reason the Action is unavailable.
welcomeTour.textDescriptions.step7: If you want to quickly perform an action, these 3 dots will become your friend. Clicking here will allow you to perform any of the available Actions that can be performed on the SIM without having to dive into the SIM Details.
welcomeTour.textDescriptions.finalStep: If you ever want to see this tour again it is available from the menu. To see a more in-depth guide of the features of the Vodafone Business Managed IoT Connectivity Platform please head over to the Help and Support pages.
